devdoc.details: Implements voting process along with winning candidate

constructor.details: Create a new ballot to choose one of 'candidateNames'.

params.endTime_: When the voting process will end
params.startTime_: When the voting process will start

didCurrentVoterVoted(uint256).details: Know whether the voter casted their vote or not. If casted get candidate object.

params.voterAadharNumber: Aadhar number of the current voter

returns.candidate_: Candidate details to whom voter casted his/her vote
returns.userVoted_: Boolean value which gives whether current voter casted vote or not

extendVotingTime(uint256,uint256).details: To extend the end of the voting

params.currentTime_: Current time that needs to be updated
params.endTime_: End time that needs to be updated

params.voterAadharNumber: Aadhar number of the current voter to send the relevent candidates list

returns._0: candidatesList_ All the politicians who participate in the election

getResults(uint256).details: sends all candidate list with their votes count

getVotingEndTime().details: Gives ending epoch time of voting

params.voterAadharNumber: Aadhar number of the current voter to send the relevent candidates list

returns.voterEligible_: Whether the voter with provided aadhar is eligible or not

updateVotingStartTime(uint256,uint256).details: used to update the voting start & end times

params.currentTime_: Current time that needs to be updated
params.startTime_: Start time that needs to be updated

params.currentTime_: To check if the election has started or not
params.voterAadharNumber: Aadhar Number of the voter to avoid re-entry
